ement with an origin in populations clustered according to\nthe standard cosmological model (LCDM) at epochs coinciding with the first\nstars era.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2012 19:40:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Apr 2012 15:06:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
