olume effects as an important ion specificity\nand a non-negligible ingredient for the stability of macromolecules in\nelectrolyte solutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2012 20:59:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
