d. This procedure brings us to the Stueckelberg theory which contains\nlocalized propagating tachyons in 4D spacetime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Jan 2012 12:06:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Nov 2012 12:54:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-11-13"}
